        <div class="v1-banner-tag">PREVIOUS EDITION</div>
        <div class="v1-banner-eyebrow">// MAY 15–19, 2026 · GLOBAL · ONLINE</div>
        <div class="v1-banner-title">JacHacks <span class="v1-banner-accent">Spring</span></div>
        <div class="v1-banner-sub">Where the series went global.</div>
        <div class="v1-stats-row">
          <div class="v1-stat">
            <span class="v1-stat-val">300+</span>
            <span class="v1-stat-key">PARTICIPANTS</span>
